                            Like Our Page
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="facebook-preview">
                        <div class="facebook-post">
                            <div class="post-header">
                                <img src="/src/images/logo.png" alt="Spread A Smile India" class="page-avatar">
                                <div class="post-info">
                                    <h4>Spread A Smile India</h4>
                                    <span class="post-time">2 hours ago</span>
